            </li>
            <li>
               <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Arts---Entertainment/Art-Sanctuary-122260903695" target="_blank">
                  Art Sanctuary @ Facebook
               </a>
            </li>
         </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="schedule" class="pb-sm">
        <h2 class="title">Schedule</h2>

         <p>
            <time datetime="2023-07-28">Friday July 28, 2023</time> <span class="text-secondary">6:00<small>pm</small> &ndash; 2:00<small>am</small> (EST)</span>
            <br>
            <time datetime="2023-07-29">Saturday July 29, 2023</time> <span class="text-secondary">6:00<small>pm</small> &ndash; 2:00<small>am</small> (EST)</span>
         </p>

         <p>
            Visit our <a href="/lineup/#schedule">Lineup Page</a> to view the festival itinerary. 
         </p>
      </section>

      <section id="lodging" class="pb-sm">
        <h2 class="title">Lodging</h2>

        <p>
            The nearest hotel to the venue is the Quality Inn & Suites.<br>
            Approximately a three minutes drive (0.9 mile), and right off of the interstate.
        </p>

        <p>
            Quality Inn & Suites University/Airport<br>
            311 E Gaulbert Ave<br>
            Louisville, KY 40208<br>
            <a href="https://www.google.com/travel/hotels/Quality%20Inn%20%26%20Suites%20University%2FAirport/entity/CgsI8tCd0ZP7x77cARAB/prices?q=Quality%20Inn%20%26%20Suites%20University%2FAirport" target="_blank">Booking Options</a>
        </p>

        <p>Several nearby vacation rentals can also be found on Airbnb and Vrbo.</p> 

        <p>
            Additional resources: <a href="https://www.gotolouisville.com/hotels" target="_blank">https://www.gotolouisville.com/hotels/</a>
        </p>
      </section>


      <section id="sponsors" class="pb-lg">
        <h2 class="title">Sponsors</h2>

        <div class="cards">
            <div class="card">
               <div class="card-header">
                  <h4 class="card-title">
                     Moon Coil Media
